'''Shoengen Coast''' was a location on [[Brosi]]. It was to the east of [[Shoengen Delta]].

Shoengen Coast was in the influence area of the [[Brosin Underground]] around [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]]. The smallest team of the Underground, thirty warriors personally led by [[Randle Clanse]], patrolled the Shoengen Coast.

